<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cut-n">cut <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /kʌt/    美 /kʌt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 伤口；切口：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Blood poured from the deep cut on his arm.
鲜血从他手臂上深深的伤口中涌出。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Using sharp scissors, make a small cut in the material.
用锋利的剪刀在这块布料上剪一个小口。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-haircut">2.★ <strong>理发 (haircut)</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 削减；减少；缩短；删节：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Big <strong>cuts</strong> have been made <strong>in</strong> the prices of medicine.
药品价格有了大幅度的下降。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The government are planning further <strong>cuts in</strong> income tax.
政府正计划进一步削减所得税。</p></div></div>